message:
Gooooood Evening Gopher Cru!

If you were at Shift last night you heard me say I'd be posting the links to where to sign up for Cru Winter Conference (CWC, C Dub C etc. etc.) and where to sign up for a scholarship!

If money is a problem, we will get you there - do not NOT sign up if money is the ONLY reason you are holding back from going.
And if you want to be considered to pie myself (pls not me, all other advertisements that I wanted to be, are false) or one of the other fireseeds in the face sign up BY TONIGHT.

*disclaimer - if you want to apply for a scholarship, you need to sign up for the conference first!

Peace n' Blessings.

Sign up here! https://www.cru.org/communities/campus/winterconference.html

$$ here! http://www.twincitiescru.com/cru-winter-conference-scholarships/
